<html>
  <head>
    <% include!("head.stpl"); %>
  </head>
  <body>
    <% include!("nav.stpl"); %>
    <main>
      <form action="/post/create" method="POST">
        <input type="textarea" name="content">
        <button>Create new post</button>
      </form>
      <p>
        Let's say you have a product, a portfolio, or just an idea you want to
        share with everyone on your own website. Before you publish it on the
        internet, you want to make it look attractive, professional, or at least
        decent to look at.
      </p>
      <ul>
      <% for post in posts { %>
        <li>id: <%= post.id %> with content: <pre><%= post.content %></pre></li>
      <% } %>
      </ul>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
